## Data and Content

### Knowledge Base Data
The knowledge base data (JSON files in `data/knowledge_base/provinces/`)
containing information about Vietnamese provinces, cities, attractions,
cuisine, festivals, and travel tips is compiled from publicly available
sources and is provided for educational and informational purposes.

### Administrative Data
Administrative information is based on the National Assembly Resolution
regarding administrative unit reorganization (Resolution 12/6/2025).

### Travel Tips
Travel tips and recommendations are compiled from various public sources
and personal experiences. While efforts have been made to ensure accuracy,
users should verify information independently before making travel decisions.

